=head1 NAME

 hpisensor -  This sample openhpi application displays sensor info for all resources with Sensor Capability

=head1 SYNOPSIS 

hpisensor [-D domain] [-t -r -x] [-e entitypath]

=head1 DESCRIPTION

hpisensor displays sensor info for all resources with Sensor Capability .

If no domain is selected, hpisensor uses a session with the default domain. The selected domain id must be configured via the openhpidclient.conf file specified in the environment.


=head1 OPTIONS

=over 2

 -D domain id    select Domain id
 -t              show Thresholds also
 -r              show Range values also
 -s              show EventState also
 -e entity path  limit to a single entity
 -x              show eXtra debug messages

=back

